# Linux Fundamentals Part 3

**Room:** [TryHackMe – Linux Fundamentals Part 3](https://tryhackme.com/room/linuxfundamentalspart3)
**Status:** Completed

## Summary
Covered process management, service control, the Nano text editor, and
task automation via cron/crontab on Linux systems.

## Key Commands
\`\`\`bash
nano myfile                      → Create/edit a file
ps aux | less                    → List running processes
systemctl stop <service>         → Stop a service
systemctl enable <service>       → Enable service on boot
fg                                → Bring backgrounded process to foreground
kill -SIGTERM <pid>              → Cleanly terminate a process
\`\`\`

